  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (NC-5 clean)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. Ten factors are fully assessed with achievedLevel meeting or exceeding requiredLevel; three factors (Use error, Test samples, Equivalency of input parameters) are scoped-out with documented rationale. Decision: Accepted on the basis of all assessed factors meeting credibility requirements and the scoped-out factors being demonstrably outside the evidentiary boundary of the submission.",
