        "description": "The CFD solver (ANSYS Fluent 2023 R2) is operated under a documented quality management system with version control, regression test suite covering hemolysis-relevant flow regimes, and traceable configuration records for all simulation runs submitted in this assessment."
      },
      "rationale": "All 13 simulation runs were executed under an ISO 9001-aligned QMS. Solver version, mesh, boundary-condition files, and post-processing scripts are archived in a version-controlled repository with commit hashes recorded in the evidence dossier. Regression tests demonstrate numerical reproducibility to within 0.3% across platforms."
