        "type": "AcceptanceCriteria",
        "name": "GCI < 2% on hemolysis index QoI for production mesh",
        "description": "Grid Convergence Index computed per Roache (1998) on three systematically refined meshes must be below 2% for the normalized hemolysis index at each of the five operating points."
      },
      "rationale": "Three meshes (3.2 M, 8.7 M, 22.1 M cells) were run at the design operating point. GCI on the hemolysis index is 1.4% (fine-to-medium) and 1.1% (medium-to-coarse extrapolated), confirming grid-independent results. Production mesh is the 8.7 M cell configuration."
    },
    {
